                     <interp inst="t18460817-1582-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> for stealing 1 handkerchief, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18460817-name-538" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18460817-name-538" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
